--
-- Rebuilt from scratch.
--
-- Public/read-only monitor for actual treasury spending and forecast public
-- payroll. It does not mutate the bank, does not tick inflation, and does not
-- display internal economy rules.
--
-- Data sources:
--   * ServerSideAccounts: status / supply / treasury_history
--   * ServerSideAccounts: list_employee_mappings / get_worker_pay_rates
--
-- What it shows:
--   * Treasury reserve and supply
--   * Recent treasury outflows by category
--   * Annualised public payroll forecast by real mapped workers
--   * Recent treasury transaction feed
-- =============================================================================

